+/** @file
+*  Plugin library for setting up dynamic PCDs for TerminalDxe, from fw_cfg
+*
+*  Copyright (C) 2015-2020, Red Hat, Inc.
+*  Copyright (c) 2014, Linaro Ltd. All rights reserved.<BR>
